data.description: Welcome to your very own oasis of tranquility and luxury living! This home boasts an expansive 19,689 square foot lot and a sparkling pool.The backyard includes a sunroom that bathes the home in natural light.Whether you're hosting a barbecue, a poolside cocktail party, or simply basking in the sun, this space will become your private paradise.The floor plan features 4 bedrooms, office, and 2.5 bathrooms with plenty of room for your family to thrive.The kitchen is a chef's dream come true. Featuring top-tier appliances, stunning granite countertops, and custom-made kitchen cabinets. Fresh paint adds a touch of modernity and elegance to this already stunning home. This home is a rare find, offering a harmonious blend of space, style, and serenity. Come and experience the luxurious living in this beautiful oasis – your dream home awaits!
